26quot%3BA%20piece%20of%20road%20that%20should've%20taken%2015%20minutes%2C%20it%20took%20us%2011%20hours%20because%20we%20went%20and%20picked%20up%20everyone%2C%20put%20them%20in%20a%20bag%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2055-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbandoned%20cars%20that%20were%20torched%20or%20riddled%20with%20bullet%20holes%20still%20litter%20the%20landscape%20of%20southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20already%20loading%20dozens%20of%20corpses%20onto%20refrigerated%20trucks%2C%20Landau%20and%20fellow%20volunteers%20reached%20Beeri%2C%20a%20kibbutz%20of%20around%201%2C200%20residents%20five%20kilometres%20(three%20miles)%20from%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20that%20I'm%20falling%20apart%2C%20not%20only%20me%2C%20my%20whole%20crew%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled%2C%20after%20entering%20the%20first%20home%20and%20finding%20a%20dead%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHer%20stomach%20was%20ripped%20open%2C%20a%20baby%20was%20there%2C%20still%20connected%20with%20the%20cord%2C%20and%20stabbed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Landau.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Zaka%20volunteer%20said%20he%20saw%20multiple%20civilians%2C%20including%20around%2020%20children%2C%20who%20had%20their%20hands%20tied%20behind%20their%20backs%20before%20being%20shot%20and%20torched.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20some%20victims%20positioned%20that%20they%20were%20sexually%20abused%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStricken%20festival%20site%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20100%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20kibbutz%2C%20while%20around%20270%20were%20left%20dead%20at%20the%20nearby%20Supernova%20music%20festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20bodies%20of%20the%20revellers%20have%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20site%2C%20their%20belongings%20were%20left%20strewn%20across%20the%20dusty%20grass.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20AFP%20journalist%20visited%20on%20Thursday%2C%20beanbags%2C%20artworks%20and%20a%20bag%20of%20energy%2