inated%20through%20the%20platform.%20There%20is%20no%20place%20on%20X%20for%20terrorist%20organisations%20or%20violent%20extremists%20groups%20and%20we%20continue%20to%20remove%20such%20accounts%20in%20real%20time%2C%20including%20proactive%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20social%20media%20platform's%20CEO%2C%20Linda%20Yaccarino.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20swift%20response%20from%20X%20was%20prompted%20by%20a%2024-hour%20ultimatum%20issued%20by%20European%20Union%20industry%20chief%20Thierry%20Breton%20to%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20urging%20him%20to%20combat%20the%20spread%20of%20disinformation%20on%20X%20and%20ensure%20compliance%20with%20new%20EU%20online%20content%20regulations.%20Breton%20voiced%20concerns%20over%20the%20platform's%20alleged%20use%20in%20distributing%20illegal%20content%20and%20disinformation%20within%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20newly%20implemented%20EU's%20Digital%20Services%20Act%20(DSA)%2C%20large%20online%20platforms%20like%20X%20and%20Meta's%20Facebook%20(META.O)%20are%20required%20to%20take%20more%20proactive%20measures%20to%20remove%20illegal%20content%20and%20address%20threats%20to%20public%20security%20and%20civic%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYaccarino%20emphasised%20that%20following%20the%20attack%2C%20X%20established%20a%20leadership%20group%20to%20evaluate%20the%20situation%20promptly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20Breton%2C%20Yaccarino%20expressed%20X's%20willingness%20to%20engage%20further%20with%20the%20EU%20and%20its%20team%2C%20including%20holding%20a%20meeting%20to%20address%20any%20specific%20concerns.%20The%20CEO%20eagerly%20awaited%20additional%20details%20to%20which%20the%20platform%20could%20respond%20effectively.%3Cbr%3E%20X%20reported%20that%20it%20had%20responded%20to%20more%20than%2080%20takedown%20requests%20from%20the%20EU%20within%20the%20required%20time%20frame%20and%20had%20not%20received%20any%20notices%20from%20Europol%20regarding%20illegal%20content%20on%20its