%20region%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20security%20concerns%20that%20continue%20to%20escalate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20a%20baby%2C%20an%20infant%20riddled%20with%20bullets.%20Soldiers%20beheaded.%20Young%20people%20burned%20alive%20in%20their%20cars%20or%20in%20their%20highway%20rooms.%20It%20almost%20defies%20comprehension%2C%26quot%3B%20Secretary%20Blinken%20expressed%20anguish%20at%20the%20barbarity%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20October%207%20in%20southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20we%20did%20see%2C%20photographs%20and%20videos%20that%2C%20the%20Israeli%20government%20shared%20with%20us...%20It's%20hard%20to%20find%20the%20right%20words.%20It's%20beyond%20what%20anyone%20would%20ever%20wanna%20imagine%20much%20less%20actually%20see%20and%20god%20forbid%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Blinken%20on%20horrific%20photographs%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20Hamas'%20use%20of%20civilians%20as%20human%20shields%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20recurring%20and%20deeply%20troubling%20tactic.%20Blinken%20emphasised%20that%20civilians%20are%20not%20the%20target%20of%20Israel's%20operations%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20Mediterranean%20situation%20in%20Gaza%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20first%20important%20to%20remember%20a%20fundamental%20issue%20that%20makes%20this%20complicated.%20Hamas%20continues%20to%20use%20civilians%20as%20human%20shields.%20Something%20that's%20not%20new%2C%20something%20that%20they've%20always%20done%20intentionally%20putting%2C%20civilians%20in%20harm's%20way%20to%20protect%20them%20to%20try%20to%20protect%20themselves%20or%20protect%20their%20structure%20or%20protect%20their%20weapons...%20Civilians%20should%20not%20be%20used%20in%20any%20way%20as%20the%20targets%20of%20military%20operations.%20They%20are%20not%20the%20target%20of%20Israel's%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20US%20Secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Secretary%20Blinken%20discussed%20efforts%20to%20address%20the%20humanitarian%20needs%20of%20the%20people%20living%20in%20Gaza%20while%20safeguarding%20them%20from%20harm%20during%20Israel's%20legitimate%20security%20operations%20aimed%20at%20defending%20itself%20from%20terrorism.%20He%20also%20explored%20the%20possibilities%20of%20providing%20safe%20passage%20for%20civilians%20who%20wish%20to%20leave%20Gaza%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20importance%20of%20protecting%20innocent%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20discuss%20ways%20to%20address%20the%20humanitarian%20needs%20of%20people%20living%20in%2C%20Gaza%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20harm%20while%20Israel%20conducts%20its%20legitimate%20security%20operations%20to%20defend%20itself%20from%20terrorism%20and%20to%20try%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20never%20happens%20again.%20We%20also%20talked%20about%2C%20possibilities%20for%20safe%20passage%20for%20civilians%20who%20want%20to%20leave%20or%20get%20out%20of%20the%20way%2C%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20that's%2C%20a%20conversation%20to%20the%20discussion%20that%20we%20will%20pursue%2C%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20including%20some%20of%20the%20countries%20that%20we'll%20be%20visiting...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20discussions%20with%20Israeli%20leadership%2C%20Secretary%20Blinken%20reaffirmed%20the%20United%20States'%20unwavering%20support%20for%20Israel's%20right%20to%20defend%20its%20people%20and%20its%20determination%20to%20prevent%20a%20recurrence%20of%20the%20tragic%20events%20that%20unfolded%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecretary%20Blinken%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20President%20Biden%2C%20also%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20preventing%20any%20further%20fronts%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20and%20warned%20against%20any%20attempts%20by%20state%20or%20non-state%20actors%20to%20exploit%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20our%20determination%20and%2C%20that%20of%20Israel%20as%20well%2C%20that%20not%20be%20a%20second%20front%20or%20a%20third%20front.%20And%20we%20are%20working%2C%20as%20hard%20as%20we%20can%2C%20working%20with%20other%20partners%20in%20the%20region%2C%20to%20try%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20case.%20President%20Biden%20has%20also%20been%20very%20clear%20that%20no%20one%2C%20state%20or%20non-state%20actor%20should%20try%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20this%20moment...%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20actively%20assisting%20Israel%20at%20its%20request%20and%20is%20committed%20to%20providing%20the%20necessary%20support%20for%20the%20nation's%20security%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident's%20been%20very%20clear%20we%20stand%20with%20Israel.%20We%20stand%20with%20Israel%20in%20its%20determination%20to%20defend%20its%20people%2C%20defend%20its%20country.%20We%20stand%20with%20Israel%20in%20its%20determination%20to%20do%20everything%20possible%20to%20ensure%20that%20what%20happened%20on%20Saturday%20never%20happens%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Israeli%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%20thanked%20Blinken%20and%20the%20US%20for%20their%20continuous%20support%20and%20added%20that%20the%20security%20and%20defence%20of%20the%20Israeli%20people%20is%20the%20highest%20priority%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20is%20clear.%20Because%20of%20that%20day%20-%20it's%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20Jews%20ever%20killed%20since%20the%20Holocaust%20-%20I%20think%20we%20must%20be%20clear%20that%20this%20is%20not%20only%20unacceptable%2C%20which%20the%20president%20said%2C%20but%20the%20sense%20of%20security%20and%20defence%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20deserve%20is%20something%20which%20is%20of%20highest%20priority%20so%20that%20these%20pictures%20will%20never%20occur%2C%26quot%3B%20Herzog%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%20also%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20and%20affirmed%20US'%20commitment%20to%20support%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20message%20that%20I%20bring%20to%20Israel%20is%20this%20--%20you%20may%20be%20strong%20enough%20on%20your%20own%20to%20defend%20yourself%2C%20but%20as%20long%20as%20America%20exists%2C%20you%20will%20never%2C%20ever%20have%20to.%20We%20will%20always%20be%20there%20by%20your%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel%20quoted%20Blinken%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20message%20that%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20delivered%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20from%20the%20moment%20that%20this%20crisis%20began%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20in%20Israel%20since%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20October%207%20has%20jumped%20to%201%2C300%20and%20some%203300%20have%20been%20injured%2C%20including%2028%20in%20critical%20condition%20and%20350%20in%20serious%20condition%2C%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel%20reported%20citing%20Hebrew%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20fate%20of%20an%20estimated%20150%20people%20abducted%20and%20taken%20to%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20during%20the%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20is%20still%20unclear%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697160720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fvb96d8e8_antony-blinken-reuters_625x300_23_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-war-antony-blinken-describes-after-seeing-murdered-babies-photos-in-hamas-attacks-on-israel-4476579%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken's%20visit%20to%20Israel%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20has%20brought%20to%20light%20the%20harrowing%20realities%20faced%20by%20civilians%20in%20the%20region%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20security%20co