resent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20got%20some%20pretty%20good%2C%20let's%20say%20qualified%2C%20contributional%20testimony%20from%20Murphy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rep.%20Russ%20Fulcher%20of%20Idaho%2C%20who%20recently%20recovered%20from%20his%20own%20bout%20of%20cancer.%20%26quot%3BHe%20said%2C%20'This%20is%20targeted%2C%20his%20medical%20regimen%20is%20one%20that%20has%20minimal%20side%20effects%2C%20he%20can%20do%20this.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20he%20addressed%20it%20is%2C%20if%20you%20get%20this%20contact%20from%20your%20constituent%2C%20you%20can%20say%2C%20'Look%20in%20today's%20world%2C%20this%20is%3Cbr%3Equite%20treatable%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Rep.%20David%20Schweikert%20of%20Arizona.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20Scalise%20and%20Murphy%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Scalise%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscalise.house.gov%2Fpress-release%2FScalise%253A-As-Speaker%252C-I%2527d-Lead-In-The-Fight-For-American-Families%5C%22%3Eaddressed%20the%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20on%20Fox%20News%20last%20week%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20the%20doctors%20didn't%20sign%20off%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20doing%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20comes%20after%20Greene%20became%20the%20first%20lawmaker%20to%20publicly%20raise%20the%20issue%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20as%20the%20House%20GOP%20conference%20struggles%20to%20unify%20behind%20a%20candidate%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20last%20week's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-mccarthy-ousted-speaker-house-first-time-history-matt-gaetz-2023-10%5C%22%3Eouster%20of%20Kevin%20McCarthy.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20supporters%20of%20Rep.%20Jim%20Jordan%20of%20Ohio%2C%20who%20lost%20to%20Scalise%20by%20a%20113-99%20margin%20during%20a%20closed-door%20vote%20on%20Thursday%2C%20have%20so%20far%20refused%20to%20support%20Scalise%2C%20li