%20do%20think%20it's%20fair%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Fulcher%2C%20who's%20supporting%20Scalise.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20that%20it%20should%20be%20discussed%20and%20disclosed%2C%20just%20like%20it%20was%20in%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurchett%2C%20one%20of%20the%20eight%20Republicans%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-mccarthy-ousted-speaker-house-first-time-history-matt-gaetz-2023-10%5C%22%3Evoted%20to%20oust%20McCarthy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20he%20even%20prayed%20for%20Scalise%20during%20a%20recent%20party%20meeting%20after%20a%20friend%20sent%20him%20a%20Bible%20verse%20from%20the%20Epistle%20of%20James%20pertaining%20to%20healing%20from%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20ticked%20off%20at%20the%20conference.%20I%20was%20going%20to%20rail%20on%20leadership%20that%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Burchett.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20I%20read%20that%20and%20I%20thought%2C%20'No.'%20So%20that's%20what%20I%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurchett%20also%20suggested%20that%20Greene%20was%20getting%20more%20attention%20for%20her%20remark%20about%20Scalise's%20cancer%20because%20she's%20a%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20lets%20you%20know%20what%20she%20thinks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Burchett.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20probably%20if%20she%20was%20the%20guy%20and%20said%20it%2C%20nobody%20would%20have%20thought%20nothing%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-scalise-blood-cancer-marjorie-taylor-greene-trump-house-speaker-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697144136000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652851236561dd877e796664%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-scalise-blood-cancer-marjorie-taylor-greene-trump-house-speaker-2023-10%22%2C%22summar