indifferent%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20have%20lost%20their%20sense%20of%20childhood.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ESince%20Hamas%20first%20attacked%20Israel%2C%20Israel%20has%20devastated%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20with%20air%20strikes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20University%20professor%20and%20father%20of%20six%20in%20Gaza%20said%20the%20current%20war%20is%20the%20most%20difficult%20time%20he%20and%20his%20fellow%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20through%20and%20that%20it's%20particularly%20hard%20on%20the%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERefaat%20Alareer%2C%20a%2044-year-old%20who%20works%20at%20Islamic%20University%20of%20Gaza%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20constant%20bombings%2C%20the%20death%2C%20and%20the%20destruction%20have%20had%20a%20stark%20impact%20on%20his%20youngest%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Hamas%2C%20which%20controls%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20first%20attacked%20Israel%20last%20Saturday%2C%20Israel%20has%20dropped%20hundreds%20of%20tons%20of%20bombs%20onto%20the%20Palestinian%20territory%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-gaza-devastation-israel-counterattack-2023-10%5C%22%3Eflattening%20mosques%20and%20neighborhoods%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20displacing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fpress-releases%2F2023%2F10%2Fisraeloccupied-palestinian-territory-un-experts-deplore-attacks-civilians%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAs%2520of%252011%2520October%252C%2520the%2Cschools%2520across%2520the%2520Gaza%2520Strip.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20residents%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20little%20ones%20are%20usually%20where%20you%20see%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20bombings%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alareer%2C%20whose%20two%20youngest%20children%20are%207%20and%2011%20years%20old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20gradual%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20first%2C%20it%20starts%20with%20fear%20and%20screaming%20and%20crying%20from%20the%20kids%20every%20time%20they%20hear%20a%20bomb.%20And%20because%20it%20never%20stops%20and%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20days%20there's%20barely%20any%20sleep.%20Even%20when%20you%20sleep%2C%20you%20get%20awakened%20by%20yet%20another%20series%20of%20bombs%20with%20the%20home%2C%20the%20building%2C%20all%20the%20whole%20building%20shaking%20and%20the%20sirens%20and%20the%20smoke%2C%20the%20gunpowder%2C%20the%20cement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bomb%20could%20be%20heard%20going%20off%20close%20to%20Alareer's%20home%20while%20he%20was%20on%20the%20phone%20with%20Insider.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20okay%20and%20that%20his%20family%20has%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20windows%20during%20the%20blasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlareer%20said%20that%20once%20his%20kids%20got%20used%20to%20the%20fear%2C%20their%20mentality%20shifted.%20They%20became%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20bit%20numb%20and%20indifferent%2C%20kind%20of%20submitting%20to%20what%20might%20come%20at%20any%20time%20in%20the%20most%20brutal%20kind%20of%20anticipation%20and%20waiting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20youngest%20children%20ask%20questions%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20a%20war%3F%26quot%3B%20Is%20this%20person%20or%20that%20person%20going%20to%20be%20okay%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAre%20we%20going%20to%20be%20okay%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20questions%20that%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20hear.%20You%20want%20your%20kids%20to%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20you%20don't%20want%20them%20to%20grow%20talking%20about%20war%20and%20death%20and%20destruction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20thing%20is%20they%20lose%20this%20kind%20of%20sense%20of%20childhood%20that%20is%20being%20playful%2C%20being%20naughty%2C%20being%20out%20there%20with%20the%20toys%20and%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20now%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20most%20often%20they%20will%20be%20sitting%20somewhere%20in%20a%20corner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlareer's%20older%20kids%20are%2014%2C%2017%2C%2020%2C%20and%2021%20years%20old.%20All%20six%20of%20them%2C%20along%20with%20Alareer%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20have%20been%20hunkered%20down%20in%20their%20apartment%20in%20Gaza%20City%20since%20the%20war%20began.%20The%20youngest%20children%20have%20not%20been%20allowed%20to%20go%20outside%2C%20Alareer%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20that%20it%20is%20safer%20inside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlareer%20said%20that%20people%20normally%20distinguish%20events%20in%20their%20lives%20by%20markers%20like%20when%20they%20traveled%20to%20that%20place%2C%20when%20they%20bought%20this%20car%2C%20and%20when%20they%20moved%20to%20a%20place%2C%20but%20not%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20has%20found%20himself%20marking%20big%20life%20events%2C%20and%20time%20itself%2C%20by%20its%20connection%20to%20war%2C%20explaining%20that%20his%207-year-old%20daughter%20is%20now%20four-wars-old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20usually%2C%20in%20Gaza%2C%20'yeah%2C%20he%20was%20born%20after%20the%20war%2C%20after%20the%20second%20war%2C%20after%20that%20war%2C%20after%20this%20war%2C'%26quot%3B%20Alareer%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20is%20in%20itself%20devastating%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20way%20how%20we%20mark%20our%20memories%20by%20not%20the%20best%2C%20but%20by%20the%20worst.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20he%20said%2C%20there's%20beauty%20in%20Palestinians'%20strong%20sense%20of%20solidarity.%20Despite%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgaza-strip-life-get-worse-israel-cut-food-fuel-power-2023-10%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520siege%2520will%2520%2522quite%2520literally%2Cor%2520get%2520food%2520and%2520water.%5C%22%3Edwindling%20supplies%20of%20food%20and%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20hasn't%20seen%20anyone%20hoarding%20or%20amassing%20more%20food%20than%20they%20need.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20at%20least%20we%20suffer%20equally%2