yA3.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20written%20to%20Meta%20chief%20executive%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20over%20their%20social%20media%20platforms%E2%80%99%20alleged%20role%20in%20%E2%80%9Caiding%20communal%20hatred%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country.%20It%20further%20demanded%20that%20the%20platforms%20maintain%20neutrality%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letters%20came%20after%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20flagged%20alleged%20bias%20of%20Facebook%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20YouTube%20towards%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20shared%20the%20letter%20to%20Zuckerberg%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CLetter%20by%20INDIA%20parties%20to%20Facebook%E2%80%99s%20Mr.%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20(%40finkd)%20citing%20the%20exhaustive%20investigations%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Meta%20is%20culpable%20of%20abetting%20social%20disharmony%20and%20inciting%20communal%20hatred%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELetter%20by%20INDIA%20parties%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffacebook%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Facebook%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20Mr.%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffinkd%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40finkd%3C%2Fa%3E)%20citing%20the%20exhaustive%20investigations%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwashingtonpost%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40washingtonpost%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Meta%20is%20culpable%20of%20abetting%20social%20disharmony%20and%20inciting%20communal%20hatred%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%5BLetter%20Below%5D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22