%3E%26quot%3BIn%20another%20article%20titled%20'Under%20India's%20pressure%2C%20Facebook%20let%20propaganda%20and%20hate%20speech%20thrive'%2C%20the%20Post%20has%20elucidated%20with%20evidence%20the%20blatant%20partisanship%20by%20Facebook%20India%20executives%20towards%20the%20ruling%20dispensation.%20This%20was%20well%20known%20to%20us%20in%20the%20Opposition%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20have%20even%20raised%20it%20several%20times%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20clear%20from%20these%20exhaustive%20investigations%20by%20the%20Washington%20Post%20that%20Meta%20is%20culpable%20of%20abetting%20social%20disharmony%20and%20inciting%20communal%20hatred%20in%20India.%20Further%2C%20we%20have%20data%20that%20shows%20algorithmic%20moderation%20and%20suppression%20of%20Opposition%20leaders'%20content%20on%20your%20platform%20while%20also%20promoting%20ruling%20party%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20sent%20by%20AICC%20general%20secretary%20organisation%20KC%20Venugopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20bloc%20demanded%20that%20Meta's%20operations%20in%20India%20remain%20neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20blatant%20partisanship%20and%20bias%20towards%20one%20political%20formation%20by%20a%20private%20foreign%20company%20is%20tantamount%20to%20interfering%20in%20India's%20democracy%2C%20one%20that%20we%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20not%20take%20lightly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20light%20of%20the%20upcoming%20national%20elections%20in%202024%2C%20it%20is%20our%20earnest%20and%20urgent%20plea%20to%20you%20to%20consider%20these%20facts%20seriously%20and%20ensure%20immediately%20that%20Meta's%20operations%20in%20India%20remain%20neutral%20and%20are%20not%20used%20wittingly%20or%20unwittingly%20to%20cause%20social%20unrest%20or%20distort%20India's%20much%20cherished%20democratic%20ideals%2C%26quo