l%20of%20these%20hoops%20that%20you%20have%20to%20jump%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20Nikhil%20Kamath%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FhjiZ11lKCrU%3Fsi%3DideTFPsYCdfMUMlv%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20because%20they%20can't%20manufacture%20more%20of%20that...they%20can%20go%20make%20a%20million%20of%20these%20bags%20and%20stuff%20but%20that%20strategy%20of%20being%20arrogant%20has%20worked%20so%20well%20for%20them%20that%20I%20think%20people%20have%20to%20be%20cognizant%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-man-shares-his-auto-driver-was-juspays-chief-growth-officer-4473760%5C%22%3EBengaluru%20Man%20Shares%20His%20Auto%20Driver%20Was%20Juspay's%20Chief%20Growth%20Officer%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKishore%20Biyani%2C%20founder%20of%20Future%20Group%20who%20was%20a%20guest%20at%20the%20show%2C%20then%20highlighted%20the%20difference%20between%20his%20approach%20with%20Big%20Bazar%20and%20the%20ultra-luxury%20brands.%20Mr%20Biyani%20stated%20that%20Big%20Bazaar%20was%20built%20on%20three%20things%20-%20fear%2C%20greed%20and%20altruism.%20He%20explained%20that%20'greed'%20is%20that%20the%20products%20are%20available%20at%20lower%20prices%20and%20%26quot%3Bfear%26quot%3B%20is%20that%20it%20won't%20be%20available%20after%20a%20while.%20All%20the%20brands%20are%20built%20on%20appealing%20to%20your%20ego%20and%20vanity%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20differentiating%20between%20Big%20Bazaar%20and%20the%20ultra-luxury%20brands%2C%20Mr%20Biyani%20said%20that%20they%20were%20going%20after%20greed%20and%20fear%20and%20the%20ultra-luxury%20brands%20were%20going%20after%20ego%20and%2