0Ms%20Robin%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20previously%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EVoice%20Of%20America%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0that%20she%20has%20done%20nothing%20wrong.%20She%20added%20that%20she%20felt%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%20on%20her%20shoulders%20as%20she%20believed%20it%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20Pakistan%20would%20have%20a%20participant%20in%20the%20global%20Miss%20Universe%20pageant.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20I%20won't%20do%20anything%20that%20would%20harm%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCyLfjUfrl7o%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCyLfjUfrl7o%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCyLfjUfrl7o%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCyLfjUfrl7o%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5