3Bdeep%20and%20emotional%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20only%20part%20of%20the%20picture%2C%20regular%20Indians.%20Look%20at%20the%20social%20media%20of%20the%20embassy.%20It's%20amazing%2C%20I%20think%20I%20could%20have%20another%20IDF%20with%20the%20volunteers.%20Everyone%20is%20telling%20me%2C%20I%20want%20to%20volunteer%2C%20I%20want%20to%20fight%20for%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20served%20in%20many%20countries%20in%20the%20world%2C%20many%20friendly%20countries.%20This%20wide%20support%2C%20strong%20support%20is%20unprecedented%20for%20me.%20I%20am%20really%20moved%20and%20touched.%20The%20closeness%20between%20Israel%20and%20India%20is%20something%20I%20cannot%20even%20explain...it's%20very%20emotional%2C%20very%20deep...it%20is%20something%20very%20unique%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20onslaught%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20on%20Gaza%20following%20Hamas%20attacks%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20on%20Tuesday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-stands-firmly-with-israel-pm-modi-after-call-with-netanyahu-4467275%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20provided%20him%20with%20an%20update%20about%20the%20ongoing%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20the%20people%20of%20India%20stand%20firmly%20with%20Israel%20in%20this%20difficult%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thank%20Prime%20Minister%20%40netanyahu%20for%20his%20phone%20call%20and%20providing%20an%20update%20on%20the%20ongoing%20situation.%20The%20people%20of%20India%20stand%20firmly%20with%20Israel%20in%20this%20difficult%20hour.%20India%20strongly%20and%20unequivocally%20condemns%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20forms%20and%20manifestations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%2C%20expressing%20solidarity%20with%20Israel%20in%20the%2