Methodological%20Issues%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20On%20Global%20Hunger%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20flawed%20measure%20of%20'hunger'%20and%20does%20not%20reflect%20India's%20true%20position%2C%20the%20government%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Global%20Hunger%20Report%202023%20released%20by%20Ireland%20non-profit%20Concern%20Worldwide%20and%20Germany's%20Welt%20Hunger%20Hilfe%20ranked%20India%20at%20111%20among%20125%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20index%20is%20an%20erroneous%20measure%20of%20hunger%20and%20suffers%20from%20serious%20methodological%20issues.%20Three%20out%20of%20the%20four%20indicators%20used%20for%20calculation%20of%20the%20index%20are%20related%20to%20the%20health%20of%20children%20and%20cannot%20be%20representative%20of%20the%20entire%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fourth%20and%20most%20important%20indicator%20'Proportion%20of%20Undernourished%20(PoU)%20population'%20is%20based%20on%20an%20opinion%20poll%20conducted%20on%20a%20very%20small%20sample%20size%20of%203%2C000%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20prioritised%20several%20key%20activities%20to%20address%20the%20challenge%20of%20malnutrition%20under%20Mission%20Saksham%20Anganwadi%20and%20Poshan%202.0%20(Mission%20Poshan%202.0).%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20developed%20and%20deployed%20the%20'Poshan%20Tracker'%20application%20as%20an%20important%20governance%20tool%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20key%20international%20organizations%20such%20as%20UNICEF%2C%20WHO%2C%20and%20the%20World%20Bank%20have%20acknowledged%20the%20'Poshan%20Tracker'%20as%20a%20game-changer%20in%20the%20area%20of%20nutrition.%20The%20World%20Bank%20and%20UNICEF%20have%20collaborated%20closely%20with%20the%20ministry%20to%20support%20the%20operationalisation%20of%20the%20'Poshan%20Tracker'%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20April%202023%2C%20the%20measurement%20data%20of%20children%20under%205%20years%20uploaded%20on%20Poshan%20Tracker%20has%20consistently%20increased%20-%20from%206.34%20crore%20in%20April%202023%20to%207.24%20crore%20in%20September%202023.%20The%20percentage%20of%20child%20wasting%2C%20as%20seen%20on%20the%20Poshan%20Tracker%2C%20has%20been%20consistently%20below%207.2%20per%20cent%2C%20month-on-month%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20value%20of%2018.7%20per%20cent%20used%20for%20child%20wasting%20in%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20indicators%20-%20stunting%20and%20wasting%20-%20are%20outcomes%20of%20complex%20interactions%20of%20various%20other%20factors%20like%20sanitation%2C%20genetics%2C%20environment%20and%20utilisation%20of%20food%20intake%20apart%20from%20hunger%20which%20is%20taken%20as%20the%20causative%20or%20outcome%20factor%20for%20stunting%20and%20wasting%20in%20the%20GHI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20there%20is%20hardly%20any%20evidence%20that%20the%20fourth%20indicator%2C%20namely%2C%20child%20mortality%20is%20an%20outcome%20of%20hunger%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%20launched%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Garib%20Kalyan%20Anna%20Yojana%20(PMGKAY)%20with%20the%20specific%20purpose%20of%20ameliorating%20the%20hardships%20faced%20by%20the%20poor%20and%20needy%20due%20to%20economic%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20the%20COVID-19%20outbreak%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697124180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Funaj21r8_rice-generic_625x300_27_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ferroneous-index-methodological-issues-india-on-global-hunger-report-4475838%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20flawed%20measure%