ately.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EQuestioned%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20Palestine%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20has%20so%20far%20been%20silent%20and%20has%20not%20criticised%20the%20Israeli%20attack%20on%20Gaza%2C%20Barghouti%20was%20critical%20%5Bof%20the%20president%5D%20and%20said%20he%20should%20have%20spoken.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20more%20critical%20of%20Germany%2C%20whose%20Chancellor%2C%20Olaf%20Scholz%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.alarabiya.net%2FNews%2Fmiddle-east%2F2023%2F10%2F12%2FGermany-s-Scholz-says-Palestinian-leader-Abbas-s-silence-on-Hamas-attacks-shameful-%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20called%20Abbas%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20%E2%80%9Cshameful%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20interview%20aimed%20to%20provide%20the%20Indian%20audience%20with%20an%20understanding%20of%20what%20the%20situation%20is%20in%20Gaza.%20While%20we%20are%20aware%20of%20what%20the%20Israelis%20are%20going%20through%2C%20as%20this%20aspect%20is%20being%20reported%20by%20the%20western%20media%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20equally%20important%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20Gaza.%20We%20need%20to%20know%20about%20them%2C%20too%2C%20otherwise%20we%20will%20not%20have%20a%20balanced%20view%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20certainly%20not%20an%20accurate%20and%20correct%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Israel%20has%20deliberately%20cut%20off%20electricity%2C%20water%2C%20food%2C%20and%20fuel%20to%20Gaza.%20So%2C%20what%20is%20life%20like%20for%20the%202.3%20million%20Palestinians%20besieged%20in%20that%20narrow%20strip%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20Mediterranean%C2%A0%20Sea%3F%20Not%20only%20are%20they%20starved%20and%20deprived%20of%20basic%20necessities%20of%20life%2C%20they%20also%20face%20continual%20heavy%20bombing%20day%20and%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20338%2C000%20people%20in%20Gaza%20have%20b