Balaji%20Gauri)%20at%20the%20Bombay%20General%20Hospital%20in%20the%20second%20season%20of%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Diaries%3C%2Fem%3E.%20She%20responds%20with%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20can%20get%20a%20samosa%2C%20an%20ice%20cream%2C%20maybe%20even%20a%20cola%2C%20but%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20minute%20without%20a%20new%20problem%20cropping%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20nature%20of%20a%20government%20hospital%20%E2%80%93%20where%20resources%20are%20finite%2C%20but%20an%20ailment%20is%20always%20around%20to%20be%20treated.%20The%20first%20season%20of%20the%20Nikkhil%20Advani%20show%20was%20a%20medical%20drama%20%E2%80%93%20a%20group%20of%20young%20doctors%20grappling%20with%20the%20eternal%20push-and-pull%20with%20the%20administration%20and%20protocol%20that%20gets%20in%20the%20way%20of%20saving%20lives%20in%20the%20ER%2C%20with%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20medical%20drama%2C%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Diaries%3A%2026%2F11%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20just%20about%20%3Cem%3Ethere%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20ticking%20most%20of%20the%20boxes%20of%20the%20genre%2C%20led%20by%20a%20maverick%20doctor%2C%20Kaushik%20Oberoi%20(Mohit%20Raina)%20whose%20method%20often%20skirts%20the%20lines%20of%20brilliant%20instinct%20and%20reckless%20daredevilry.%20Surrounded%20by%20superiors%20who%20bat%20for%20his%20ways%2C%20rookies%20(Natasha%20Bharadwaj%2C%20Satyajeet%20Dubey%20and%20Mrunmayee%20Deshpande)%20who%20look%20up%20to%20him%2C%20Dr.%20Oberoi%20is%20emboldened%20to%20listen%20to%20his%20gut%20rather%20than%20following%20protocol%20to%20treat%20patients.%20It%20lent%20itself%20to%20a%20superb%20conflict%20in%20the%20first%20season%2C%20when%20the%20hotshot%20doctor%20tries%20to%20revive%20a%20gravely%20injured%20terrorist%20who%20shot%20a%20cop%2C%20after%20the%20cop%E2%80%99s%20condition%20goes%20beyond%20medical%20help.%20There%E2%80%99s%20resistance%20from%20within%20the%20hospital%20staff%2C%20cops%2C%20and%20even%20the%20slain%20cop%E2%80%99s%20spouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20season%20begins%20a%20few%20months%20after%20the%20events%20of%20the%20first%20season%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20torrential%20downpour%20the%20city%20is%20known%20for.%20Even%20though%20the%20show%E2%80%99s%20events%20lie%20somewhere%20in%20June%202009%2C%20it%20uses%20the%20events%20of%20the%202005%20floods%20that%20ravaged%20the%20city%2C%20as%20the%20springboard%20for%20events%20in%20the%20second%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgnBcdm_KkYs%3Fsi%3DabeMsGakF5j6nCtg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr.%20Oberoi%20is%20being%20investigated%20for%20%E2%80%9Cmedical%20negligence%E2%80%9D%20after%20a%20high-ranking%20cop%20died%20on%20a%20stretcher%20in%20front%20of%20him%2C%20in%20the%20first%20season.%20Patients%20are%20coming%20in%20by%20the%20dozens%20because%20of%20the%20floods%2C%20some%20injured%20because%20of%20road%20accidents%2C%20some%20picking%20up%20an%20illness%20after%20wading%20through%20drain%20water%20for%20hours.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20British%20delegation%20at%20the%20hospital%20%E2%80%93%20forcing%20hospital%20authorities%20to%20mask%20their%20significant%20infrastructure%20challenges.%20There%20are%20fewer%20doctors%20than%20needed%2C%20given%20the%20steady%20inflow%20of%20patients%20from%20all%20over%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20and%20barely%20any%20time%20for%20anything%20else.%20And%20yet%2C%20most%20doctors%20at%20the%20Bombay%20General%20Hospital%20seem%20to%20find%20time%20for%20profound%20epiphanies.%20In%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Diaries%3C%2Fem%3E%20S02%2C%20there%20are%20only%20two%20types%20of%20characters%3A%20the%20crusaders%2C%20who%20think%20aloud%20about%20their%20sense%20of%20duty%2C%20and%20the%20others%20who%20object.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20the%20TV%20anchor%20Mansi%20Hirani%20(Shreya%20Dhanwanthary)%20who%20insists%20that%20Mumbaikars%20inconvenienced%20by%20record-breaking%20rains%20and%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20crumbling%20infrastructure%20is%20not%20an%20%E2%80%98important%E2%80%99%20story.%20When%20a%20segment%20of%20her%20interviewing%20a%20martyr%E2%80%99s%20wife%20(played%20by%20Sonali%20Kulkarni)%20is%20cancelled%20%E2%80%93%20she%20raises%20her%20voice%20like%20someone%20with%20straight-out-of-journalism-school%20idealism.%20As%20much%20as%20I%20get%20her%20personal%20stake%20in%20a%20story%20she%20feels%20passionately%20about%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20marvel%20at%20her%20lack%20of%20professional%20judgment%20that%20is%20obtuse%20enough%20to%20think%20there%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20two%20equally%20important%20news%20items%20in%20a%20story%20rundown.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20younger%20doctors%20%E2%80%93%20like%20Dr.%20Ajawale%20(played%20by%20Mrunmayee%20Deshpande)%20%E2%80%94%20are%20simply%20unable%20to%20make%20even%20a%20single%20sophisticated%20argument%20against%20watching%20their%20patients%20slowly%20drift%20away%20in%20front%20of%20their%20eyes%2C%20while%20being%20told%20to%20follow%20protocol%20and%20obey%20orders%20from%20senior%20doctors.%20Dr.%20Oberoi%20%E2%80%93%20the%20star%20from%20the%20trauma%20unit%20in%20the%20first%20season%20%E2%80%93%20is%20left%20to%20doubt%20his%20natural%2C%20life-saving%20instincts%2C%20after%20being%20lynched%20in%20public%20perception%20with%20the%20help%20of%20news%20channels%20and%20social%20media%20for%20his%20reckless%20ways.%20Raina%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20most%20gifted%20actor%2C%20but%20uses%20his%20space%20well%20to%20reflect%20Dr%20Oberoi%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20believe%20his%20gift%2C%20after%20being%20questioned%20about%20it%20over%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20nice%20flourishes%20in%20the%20second%20season%2C%20like%20Konkona%20Sen%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20Chitra%20Das%2C%20haunted%20by%20her%20abusive%20marriage.%20As%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20one%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20delegation%20is%20her%20abusive%20husband%20%E2%80%93%20Dr.%20Saurav%20Chandra%20(played%20by%20Parambrata%20Chattopadhyay).%20The%20track%20is%20well-designed%2C%20giving%20us%20flashbacks%20of%20his%20erratic%20behaviour%2C%20keeping%20us%20guessing%20as%20to%20whether%20he%E2%80%99s%20here%20to%20get%20her%20back%2C%20or%20has%20he%20evolved%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChitra%20is%20reminded%20by%20her%20well-wishers%20of%20symptoms%20of%20domestic%20abuse%20%E2%80%93%20where%20victims%20often%20feel%20enamoured%20by%20sudden%20bursts%20of%20kindness%20from%20their%20abuser%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20ambiguity%20that%20keeps%20this%20section%20lively%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Sen%20Sharma%20is%20clearly%20the%20most%20refined%20actor%20in%20this%20cast%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20show%20makes%20good%20use%20of%20her.%20She%20has%20an%20admirer%20in%20young%20resident%20Dr.%20Ahaan%20Mirza%20(Satyajeet%20Dubey)%2C%20challenging%20the%20convention%20of%20an%20office%20romance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Diaries%3A%2026%2F11%3C%2Fem%3E%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20most%20competent%20medical%20drama%2C%20however%2C%20what%20made%20it%20compelling%20was%20how%20it%20viewed%20a%20terror%20attack%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20a%20crumbling%20government%20hospital.%20The%20action%20sequences%20in%20the%20first%20season%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20of%20the%20terrorists%20storming%20a%20hospital%20%E2%80%93%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20memorable%20parts%20of%20the%20first%20season.%20In%20the%20second%20season%20%E2%80%93%20with%20terrorists%20out%20of%20the%20equation%20%E2%80%93%20the%20show%20only%20relies%20on%20the%20social%20justice%20commentary.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20where%20it%20seems%20to%20falter%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20web%20series%20these%20days%2C%20even%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Diaries%3C%2Fem%3E%20S02%20stacks%20itself%20with%20social%20issues%20to%20be%20addressed.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20burns%20victim%2C%20exhibiting%20habits%20of%20someone%20using%20drugs.%20There%E2%80%99s%20an%20orphanage%20where%20the%20kids%20seem%20to%20be%20showcasing%20signs%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20%E2%80%93%20making%20the%20doctors%20suspicious%2C%20and%20therefore%20forcing%20them%20to%20go%20beyond%20their%20usual%20call%20of%20duty.%20The%20show%20even%20touches%20upon%20the%20mockery%20that%20TV%20news%20has%20become%20in%20recent%20times%20%E2%80%93%20deliberately%20doling%20out%20stories%20of%20%E2%80%9Chope%E2%80%9D%20and%20fetishising%20the%20%E2%80%9CMumbai%20spirit%E2%80%9D%20even%20as%20dozens%20of%20locals%20stare%20death%20in%20the%20face.%20A%20scene%20that%20recreates%20the%20FOB%20collapse%20and%20the%20stampede%20triggered%20by%20it%20at%20Dadar%20station%2C%20is%20easily%20one%20of%20the%20most%20tense%20sequences%20in%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20show%20never%20really%20dwells%20on%20it%20for%20long.%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Diaries%3C%2Fem%3E%20might%20pretend%20to%20be%20more%20evolved%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20actually%20a%20stitched-up%20version%20of%20many%20%3Cem%3EGeneral%20Hospital%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EE.R%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EGrey%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Es%20Anatomy%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EChicago%20P.D.%3C%2Fem%3E%20episodes.%20At%20its%20core%2C%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Diaries%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20soap%20opera.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20the%20sophistication%20of%20some%20excellent%20medical%20dramas%20like%20%3Cem%3EHouse%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20where%20doctors%20don%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20be%20losing%20their%20cool%20so%20frequently%2C%20especially%20in%20challenging%20situations.%20The%20%E2%80%98doctors%E2%80%99%20in%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Diaries%3C%2Fem%3E%20S02%20yell%20at%20each%20other%2C%20plead%20with%20one%20another%2C%20just%20like%20the%20actors%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Diaries%20S02%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20someone%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20show%20everyone%20that%20at%20Bombay%20General%20Hospital%20%E2%80%93%20our%20work%20does%20the%20talking.%E2%80%9D%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20smile%20a%20little.%20The%20sad%20part%20was%20that%20they%20were%20being%20earnest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697120955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12195615%2Fimage-1383.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmumbai-diaries-s02-looks-like-a-weighty-hospital-drama-but-is-a-soap-opera-at-heart%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20some%20good%20moments%20in%20this%20show%2C%20which%20are%20set%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20floods.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmumbai-diaries-s02-looks-like-a-weighty-hospital-drama-but-is-a-soap-opera-at-heart%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Right%20balance%20to%20promote%20sustainability%2C%20competition%20is%20pertinent%3A%20NCLAT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697120821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F12%2Ffull%2F1697120620-4822.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fright-balance-to-promote-sustainability-competition-is-pertinent-nclat-123101201175_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20was%20delivering%20the%20keynote%20address%20at%20the%20eighth%20BRICS%20International%20Competition%20Conference%202023%20in%20Delhi%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fright-balance-to-promote-sustainability-competition-is-per