20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20of%20Chandrayaan%203%20on%2013%20July%2C%202023%2C%20was%20celebrated%20at%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20in%20Sriharikota%2C%20with%20ISRO%20chairman%20S%20Somanath%20confirming%20the%20successful%20launch.%20Millions%20of%20Indians%20across%20the%20country%20watched%20this%20historic%20event%20live%2C%20and%20behind%20the%20chairman%2C%20two%20key%20figures%20of%20the%20mission%20stood%20%E2%80%94%20Mohana%20Kumar%2C%20the%20mission%20director%2C%20and%20P%20Veeramuthuvel%2C%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20project%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVeeramuthuvel%2C%20the%20cynosure%20of%20all%20eyes%2C%20stood%20with%20a%20composed%20demeanour%2C%20smiling%20and%20applauding%20as%20his%20team%E2%80%99s%20years%20of%20dedication%20paid%20off.%20Meanwhile%2C%20more%20than%20250%20kilometres%20away%20in%20Viluppuram%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20his%20proud%20family%20celebrated%20with%20fireworks%20and%20sweets%20at%20the%2046-year-old%E2%80%99s%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20as%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20is%20working%20on%20Gaganyaan%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20manned%20mission%20to%20space%2C%20P%20Veeramuthuvel%2C%20recently%20said%20at%20an%20event%20that%20they%20are%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20launch.%20%E2%80%9CGaganyaan%20programme%20is%20coming%20up.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20human%20exploration%20programme.%20We%20have%20the%20roadmap%20and%20we%20will%20have%20the%20launch%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20test%20flight%20of%20Gaganyaan%20is%20scheduled%20for%2021%20October%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20an%20average%20student%20to%20a%20topper%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20635px)%20100vw%2C%20635px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMuthuvel-1697118830.jpg