%80%99s%20husband%2C%20Om%20Prakash%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20innovated%20a%20three-layer%20approach%20to%20grow%20vegetables%20that%20utilises%20extra%20space%20in%20the%20farm.%20We%20grow%20plants%20like%20lemon%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(blackcurrants)%20in%20the%20outermost%20layer.%20In%20the%20second%20layer%2C%20we%20grow%20shorter%20plants%20like%20aloe%20vera%20that%20are%20grown%20under%20the%20shade%20of%20these%20trees.%20In%20the%20third%20layer%2C%20we%20grow%20tall%20trees%20like%20papaya%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebel%3C%2Fem%3E%20(stone%20apple)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Eamla%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20one%20place%2C%20we%20have%20planted%20three%20kinds%20of%20plants.%20We%20did%20this%20so%20that%20farmers%20understood%20they%20could%20generate%20additional%20income%20from%20the%20same%20land.%20%3Cem%3EKam%20lagat%20me%20adhik%20upaj%2C%20adhik%20upaj%20ka%20adhik%20munafa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(More%20produce%20at%20less%20input%20costs%20which%20in%20turn%20gets%20more%20profits)%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2047-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRubi-Pareek-1697117008.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rubi%20has%20also%20trained%20at%20least%2015%2C000%20farmers%20and%20agriculture%20students.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRubi-Pareek-1697117008.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRubi-Pareek-1697117008-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRubi-Pareek-1697117008-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRubi-Pareek-1697117008-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F