ver-pricing%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20said%20it%20has%20been%20vindicated%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI%E2%80%99s)%20decision%20this%20year%20to%20withdraw%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20case%20against%20one%20of%20the%2040%20importers%20named%20in%202016.%20It%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20issue%20of%20overvaluation%20in%20the%20import%20of%20coal%20was%20conclusively%20settled%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20highest%20court%20of%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20cites%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunresolved%20nature%20of%20the%20DRI%20investigation%20and%20the%20apparent%20continuation%20of%20the%20alleged%20practices%E2%80%9D%20raising%20%E2%80%9Cfresh%20questions%20about%20the%20relationship%20between%20Adani%20and%20the%20administration%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWatchdog%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20role%20too%20has%20come%20in%20the%20limelight%20after%20it%20emerged%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1055231%2Fsebi-knew-about-allegations-against-adani-group-since-2014-letter-shows%5C%22%3Eit%20knew%20about%20allegations%20against%20Adani%20Group%20since%202014%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20letter%20which%20was%20part%20of%20the%20OCCRP-%3Cem%3EFT-The%20Guardian%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20investigation%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recent%20scandal%20to%20hit%20Adani%20were%20allegations%20that%20the%20chairman%20of%20SEBI%20at%20that%20time%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnow%20an%20independent%20director%20of%20Adani-owned%20NDTV.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20raised%20three%20key%20points%20in%20its%20investigation%2C%20after%20looking%20at%2030%20shipments%20of%20coal%20from%20Indonesia%20to%20India%20by%20an%20Adani%20company%20over%2032%20months%20between%202019%20and%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20rejected%20charges%20of%20wrongdoing.%20Adani%20h