ed%20that%20mutual%20acquiescence%20in%20a%20communal%20vitiated%20atmosphere%20where%20one%20side%20was%20dominant%20was%20meaningless.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fgujarat-dargah-inside-the-complex-pavgadh-temple-harmony-of-faiths-7974241%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edargah%20at%20Pavagadh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20Uma%20Bharti%20claimed%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20debates%20on%20the%20Place%20of%20Worship%20Bill%2C%20hurt%20her%20sentiments%2C%20has%20now%20been%20removed%20by%20%E2%80%9Cmutual%20consent%E2%80%9D%2C%20enabling%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20unfurl%20a%20triumphal%20flag%20atop%20the%20temple%20spire.%20One%20can%20only%20presume%20that%20this%20was%20much%20like%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onlinevolunteers.org%2Fgujarat%2Freports%2Frural%2Frural-gujarat-04.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecompros%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20that%20enabled%20Muslim%20villagers%20to%20return%20to%20their%20villages%20after%20the%202002%20pogroms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20perhaps%20all%20is%20not%20lost%20in%20this%20country.%20In%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fhindus-sikhs-came-together-punjab-barnala-villages-build-mosques-communal-harmoney-2420122-2023-08-12%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Sikhs%20of%20Punjab%20have%20restored%20mosques%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20were%20abandoned%20after%20Muslims%20migrated%20to%20Pakistan.%20It%20is%20this%20model%20that%20we%20need%20to%20emulate%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20seeks%20to%20promote%20communal%20harmony%20in%20the%20present%20%E2%80%93%20rather%20than%20the%20revanchist%20and%20illiterate%20model%20promoted%20by%20the%20RSS.%20But%20for%20this%2C%20the%20courts%20must%20respect%20the%20faith%20of%20all%20Indians%2C%20and%20above%20all%2C%20respect%20the%2