f%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664935%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Av%20Jolanda%20Flubacher%2FWORLD%20ECONOMIC%20FORUM%2Fswiss-image.ch.%20CC%20BY-SA%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20Israeli%20leader%20has%20been%20as%20steadfast%20in%20sidelining%20the%20Palestinian%20issue%20as%20Netanyahu.%20Even%20Golda%20Meir%E2%80%99s%20execrable%20remark%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20was%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20Palestinians%E2%80%9D%20existed%20alongside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fjpost.com%2Fisrael-news%2Farticle-753212%5C%22%3Ea%20realisation%20that%20a%20Palestinian%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20to%20come%20into%20existence.%20Netanyahu%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20never%20acknowledged%20the%20need%20for%20such%20a%20thing.%20He%20called%20Yitzhak%20Rabin%2C%20who%20signed%20the%20Oslo%20Accords%20with%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fmarking-25-years-since-rabin-killing-netanyahu-says-he-is-now-pm-under-threat%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CNazi%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ctraitor%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20attended%20a%20rally%20with%20a%20coffin%20and%20noose%20for%20Rabin.%20The%20assassination%20of%20Rab