as%20even%20has%20the%20right%20to%20take%20prisoners%20of%20war%20%E2%80%93%20as%20long%20as%20they%20are%20military%20personnel%20and%20treated%20humanely.%20There%20is%20no%20right%2C%20ever%2C%20to%20commit%20war%20crimes.%20This%20applies%20to%20Israel%20as%20well%2C%20which%20routinely%20assaults%2C%20kidnaps%2C%20tortures%2C%20and%20murders%20Palestinian%20civilians.%20Every%20single%20Palestinian%20held%20in%20Israeli%20jails%2C%20whether%20charged%20by%20military%20courts%20or%20under%20%E2%80%9Cadministrative%20detention%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20illegally%20held.%20International%20law%20forbids%20the%20removal%20of%20people%20from%20an%20area%20under%20military%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fkidnapping-civilians-from-israel-hamas-war-crime%5C%22%3ELet%20Us%20Be%20Clear%2C%20the%20Kidnapping%20of%20Civilians%20from%20Israel%20By%20Hamas%20is%20a%20War%20Crime%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJew%2C%20Arab%2C%20Muslim%2C%20Christian%2C%20atheist%2C%20whatever%2C%20none%20of%20that%20matters.%20Human%20rights%20apply%20to%20all%20humans%20or%20they%20are%20worth%20nothing.%20It%20is%20both%20remarkable%20and%20deeply%20sad%20that%20courageous%20Israelis%20like%20Haggai%20Matar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fgaza-attack-context-israelis%2F%5C%22%3Ecling%20to%20these%20concepts%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20try%20to%20hide%20from%20rocket%20fire.%20And%20past%20comprehension%20that%20commentators%20in%20the%20US%20and%20parts%20of%20Europe%20would%20exclude%20the%20long%20history%20of%20war%20crimes%20by%20Israelis%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20as%20the%20Israeli%20leadership%20explicitly%20carries%20out%20further%20war%20crimes%20like%20depriving%20a%20largely%20civilian%20population%20of%20water%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F10%2F830-dead-in-gaza-since-saturday-as-shelling-hits-school-hospitals-and-homes%5