e%20chairman%20of%20the%20Commission%20of%20the%20African%20Union%20(which%20joined%20the%20G20%20as%20a%20full%20member%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20presidency)%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CDenial%20of%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20particularly%20that%20of%20an%20independent%20and%20sovereign%20State%2C%20is%20the%20main%20cause%20of%20the%20permanent%20Israeli-Palestinian%20tension.%E2%80%9D%20Japan%20(which%20may%20or%20may%20not%20count%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Global%20South)%2C%20while%20condemning%20the%20attack%20on%20civilians%20and%20hostage-taking%2C%20also%20expressed%20concern%20for%20the%20violence%20against%20civilians%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20one%20country%20or%20institution%20in%20the%20Global%20South%20with%20any%20significant%20power%20either%20followed%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20lead%20or%20agreed%20with%20his%20response.%20Almost%20all%20of%20them%20are%20in%20line%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcong-balancing-act-condemns-brutal-attack-affirms-old-stand-on-palestine-8974107%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhindutva-israel-tweets-palestine-conflict%5C%22%3EUnpacking%20the%20Hindutva%20Embrace%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Humiliation%20of%20Arab%20states%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20commentators%20have%20said%20that%20the%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20was%20intended%20to%20derail%20the%20normalisation%20of%20relations%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20Arab%20states%2C%20particularly%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20It%20has%20certainly%20put%20paid%20to%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2023-09-22%2Fty-article%2Ffull-text-benjamin-netanyahus-2023-un-general-assembly-speech%2F0000018a-bd3c-d490-adca-fdff21270000%5C%22%3Ecrude%20p