econdary%20research%2C%20but%20largely%20extrapolation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeeply%20disturbed%20by%20the%20rampant%20littering%20and%20indiscriminate%20disposal%20of%20garbage%2C%20Kandelwal%20started%20the%20%E2%80%98Maka%20Naka%20Plastic%E2%80%99%20campaign%20in%20October%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMaka%20naka%20plastic%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20plastic%E2%80%99%20in%20Konkani%2C%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20official%20language.%20The%20campaign%20involves%20making%20different%20types%20of%20bags%20from%20pre-loved%20fabric%20which%20is%20collected%20through%20collection%20drives%20at%20Sensible%20Earth%20and%20also%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20city%20corporation%20of%20Panaji.%20They%20use%20social%20media%20and%20newspapers%20as%20means%20to%20ask%20citizens%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307217%2Fyobler-platform-sells-preloved-used-baby-products-toys-clothes-bedding-sustainability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edonate%20pre-loved%20clothes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20journey%20from%20complaining%20to%20catalysing%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20take%20away%20the%20right%20only%20to%20complain%20and%20start%20doing%20something%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Khandelwal%2C%20a%2059-year-old%20serial%20entrepreneur%2C%20early-stage%20investor%2C%20and%20mentor%20to%20tech%20startups%2C%20who%20has%20a%20rich%20history%20in%20the%20internet%20sector.%20He%20played%20a%20pioneering%20role%20in%20developing%20B2B%20marketplaces%2C%20wireless%20networks%2C%20and%20dynamic%20pricing%20engines.%20His%20noteworthy%20work%20even%20became%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20case%20study%20at%20IMD%20in%20Lausanne.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20738px)%20100vw%