%22%3Eactively%20collecting%20glass%20jars%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20having%20already%20collected%202%2C000%20with%20a%20target%20of%20reaching%2010%2C000.%20Khandelwal%20points%20out%20that%20recycling%20glass%20can%20have%20a%20higher%20environmental%20impact%2C%20so%2C%20they%20have%20launched%20a%20campaign%20to%20collect%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20store%20glass%20jars%20in%20collaboration%20with%20local%20self-help%20groups.%20They%20are%20now%20exploring%20ways%20to%20repurpose%20these%20jars%20within%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20food%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhandelwal%20maintains%20that%20this%20battle%20with%20plastic%20or%20waste%2C%20in%20general%2C%20is%20a%20long-drawn%20affair%2C%20and%20there%20is%20an%20ongoing%20need%20to%20raise%20awareness.%20He%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20changing%20the%20perception%20of%20Goa%2C%20which%20is%20often%20solely%20associated%20with%20fun%20and%20enjoyment.%20This%20perception%20puts%20tremendous%20pressure%20on%20waste%20management%20and%20the%20environment%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20fact%20that%20Goa%20receives%20four%20times%20more%20tourists%20than%20its%20actual%20population%20(15%20lakhs).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20change%20the%20narrative%20of%20tourism%20in%20Goa.%20It%20is%20a%20biodiversity%20hotspot%2C%20an%20extremely%20fragile%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20one%20has%20to%20walk%20carefully%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Khandelwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWritten%20by%20Arti%20Das%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Arti%20Das.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpcb.nic.in%2Fuploads%2Fplasticwaste%2FAnnual_Report_2019-20_PWM.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnnual%20Report%202019-20%20on%20Impl