s%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nikhil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20communities%20in%20the%20Himalayas%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENikhil%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20concentrated%20in%20seven%20villages%20across%20the%20country%2C%20five%20of%20which%20are%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20In%202019%2C%20Nikhil%20adopted%20three%20villages%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%94%20Furkiyajhala%2C%20Khirdwari%20and%20Lodiyalsera%2C%20where%20he%20recognised%20an%20urgent%20need%20for%20awareness%20on%20topics%20such%20as%20menstruation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20we%20distributed%20more%20than%20100%20pads%20in%20Lodiyalsera%20and%20Khirdwari%20villages.%20The%20village%20women%20were%20not%20familiar%20with%20the%20concept%20until%20then%2C%20but%20post%20our%20drive%2C%20they%20are%20actively%20buying%20pads%20and%20using%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAnsRzO7z42g%3Fsi%3DcHUKOKiMVsQaDRzm%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%20%3Cp%3ENikhil%20recalls%20an%20incident%20prior%20to%20the%20drive%2C%20where%20Laxmi%20Devi%20from%20Khirdwari%20village%2C%20a%20woman%20in%20her%20forties%2C%20shared%20how%20periods%20are%20perceived%20in%20the%20village.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284174%2Fmenstruation-periods-girls-school-dropout-whisper%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520India%252C%2520a%2520woman%2527s%2Clakhs%2520of%2520women%2520for%2520centuries.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen%20on%20their%20period%3C%2Fa%3E%20must%20sit%20outside%20the%20home.%20We%20give%20them%20food%20but%20they%20mustn%E2%80%99t%20touch%20any%20of%20the%20utensils.%20On%20the%20fourth%20day%2C%20they%20can%20drink%20cow%20urine%20and%20then%20enter%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20appalled%20Nikhil%2C%20who%20now%20shares%20that%20Laxmi%20Devi%E2%80%99s%20views%20have%20changed%20since%20then.%20As%20she%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CNikhil%20and%20his%20team%20of%20Planet%20Trotter%20helped%20us%20get%20necessary%20medicines%20and%20pads%20and%20education%20about%20menstruation.%20Now%20we%20buy%20pads%20from%20the%20village%20shop.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENikhil%20and%20his%20team%20frequently%20distribute%20books%20and%20educational%20materials%20to%20students%20of%20the%20government-run%20schools%20in%20all%20three%20villages.%20To%20date%2C%20they%20have%20helped%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20than%20500%20students%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20such%20trip%20in%202019%2C%20Nikhil%20came%20across%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enon-functional%20computers%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20school%2C%20and%20he%20enquired%20about%20it.%20He%20was%20told%20that%20these%20had%20not%20been%20working%20for%20nine%20years%20as%20the%20electricity%20requirements%20could%20not%20be%20met.%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20six%201.5%20kW%20solar%20panels%20installed%20in%20the%20school%20which%20ensure%20the%20smooth%20functioning%20of%20the%20computers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20solar%20panels%20installed%20in%20the%20school%20are%20now%20used%20to%20power%20the%20computers%20that%20lay%20dysfunctional%20for%20years%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331887%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20solar%20panels%20installed%20in%20the%20school%20are%20now%20used%20to%20power%20the%20computers%20that%20lay%20dysfunctional%20for%20years%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nikhil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESarita%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Class%206%20who%20loves%20spending%20time%20surfing%20the%20web%20at%20school%2C%20says%20she%20spends%20her%20time%20learning%20%E2%80%98Microsoft%20Paint%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Word%E2%80%99%20among%20other%20applications%20on%20these%20refurbished%20computers%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20now%20learn%20typing%20and%20do%20so%20much%20more.%20Otherwise%2C%20we%20had%20to%20go%2070%20km%20away%20from%20the%20village%20to%20use%20the%20computer%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20Nikhil%20has%20also%20helped%20the%20villagers%20learn%20bee%20farming%2C%20which%20further%20boosts%20their%20income.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20given%20them%20boxes%20which%20they%20use%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F175651%2Findia-beekeeping-pune-kvic-bee-conservation-diy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollect%20honey%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20villagers%20were%20able%20to%20sell%20the%20honey%20at%20Rs%20450%20per%20kg%20and%20we%20are%20now%20looking%20to%20help%20them%20sell%20their%20product%20directly%20to%20the%20markets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20as%20Nikhil%20attempts%20to%20expand%20his%20platform%20in%20the%20face%20of%20stiff%20competition%20from%20other%20similar%20businesses%2C%20he%20says%20his%20idea%20is%20rooted%20in%20a%20desire%20to%20see%20the%20people%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20villages%20uplifted.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hope%20I%E2%80%99m%20able%20to%20do%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20before%20signing%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696946015000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nikhil%20Pratap%20Singh%20started%20'Planet%20Trotter'%20as%20a%20way%20to%20encourage%20slow%20and%20experiential%20travel%20while%20helping%20people%20in%20rural%20India%20earn.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331882%2Fslow-experiential-travel-startup-planet-trotter-helps-uttarakhand-villagers-vacation-plan%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NTPC%20Announces%20Job%20Vacancies%20for%20Engineers%20With%20Salary%20Upto%20Rs%20140000%20per%20Month%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Thermal%20Power%20Corporation%20(NTPC)%20is%20inviting%20applications%20for%20the%20post%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331506%2Fisro-vssc-thiruvananthapuram-jobs-apprentice-training-engineers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%2